      <title>Authors&#x2019; contributions</title>
      <p>NM performed the histological examination and diagnosis of the patient. LR and VE conducted a thorough literature review of duplication of the limbs in the human tract and were the major contributors to the writing of the manuscript. All authors read and approved the final manuscript.</p>
    </sec>
